# ─── Zendesk ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# App registration: https://developer.zendesk.com/api-reference/ticketing/oauth/oauth_clients/
# Redirect URI: https://api.crescendo.run/connections/oauth/zendesk/callback
# Note: Replace {subdomain} with your actual Zendesk subdomain in the URLs below.
